"  Streusel topping:","2/3 cups pecans, almonds or walnuts, finely chopped","1/3 cup packed light brown sugar","1/2 teaspoon ground cinnamon","2 tablespoons unsalted butter, melted","  Muffins:","4 tablespoons (1/2 stick) unsalted butter, melted and cooled","2/3 cup sugar","2  large eggs","1 teaspoon vanilla extract","1 cup plain low-fat yogurt","2 cups all-purpose flour","1 teaspoon baking powder","1/2 teaspoon baking soda","1 teaspoon cinnamon","1/2 teaspoon salt"